element.name: Sidetracked - Lansdowne DART by Hezekiah, Traditional Cache (1/1)

center.font: Visit the new Geocaching Ireland discussion forum HERE

long-description.p: The DART (Dublin Area Rapid Transit) is the rail line running along the coast of Dublin, from Malahide and Howth southwards as far as Greystones, Co Wicklow.

Side-Tracked Caches are intended to provide quick cache-and-dashes at train stations.
The Cache is a small micro container - please re-hide it well to ensure that the commuting muggles don’t discover it.

ul.li:
2010-05-08T19:00:00Z : Found it by Mac Aroni Senior
Easily found today. Muggle builder very close by (working a meter and a half away) but never noticed a thing! [:D] TFTC

2010-04-18T19:00:00Z : Found it by orangetigerprawn
I got this one while doing a few caches in the city today. There were a couple of building workers loitering nearby so it tool a little longer than expected.
Go raibh maith agat as an taisce.

2010-04-13T19:00:00Z : Found it by Calypso62
#229 This was our last cache find in Ireland. We have spent the last 8 days travelling around this beautiful country, seeing wonderful things and meeting great people. We will take away lots of happy memories. A quick find in the evening with Smurfyguy and Geotooter. Many thanks for the cache. I enjoyed travelling on the DART. G'day from Down-Under.

2010-04-13T19:00:00Z : Found it by Smurfyguy
#206 Greetings from Sydney, Australia. Found with Calypso62 and Geotooter. Nice quick find while returning from our day trip to Dublin. TNLNSL TFTC

2010-04-12T19:00:00Z : Found it by 3-guineas
Busy, dusty place. Last day in Dublin, we won't be able to see all Sidetracks. TFTC

2010-04-03T19:00:00Z : Write note by Kersti.com
Visited today with EdwardsClan. I've already logged this one, so just a note that it's in place.

2009-12-14T20:00:00Z : Found it by Kersti.com
Was on my way to an appointment and as I passed realised that I was running early - figured I'd kill some time looking for this. Barely made a dent so I ended up at a cafe regardless!

2009-07-26T19:00:00Z : Didn't find it by Kersti.com
Had a good hunt around with almost 0 muggle activity but was still unable to locate this one. Given the previous log I'm suspicious that this one has migrated out of reach.
